# Google OAuth2 client ID for Drive sync.
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/ → APIs & Services → Credentials
# 2. Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# 3. Add your origin (e.g. http://localhost:5173) to Authorized JavaScript origins
# 4. Enable the Google Drive API for your project
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your client ID.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
